{
  "id": "RAW_16ded95f",
  "title": "马耳他：向全民发放免费 ChatGPT 会员",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247517066&idx=1&sn=0b407e1797ba301455ccb1ff42e8eb04",
  "date": "2026-05-16 11:38:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>金色传说大聪明</span> <span>2026-05-16 19:38</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=32e200f7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FjXSGuwJvpdhvQMSqXKFyguf6KKQ1J58d3vXXdDibebldTn10nfn0hY5bz8zKqumTTthQiaycichsjdUtssEV2VIP5vLToBEcrZLtXibdjtibW8hs%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>注：马耳他是个欧洲国家</p>\n  <div style=\"background:rgba(26,26,24,0.02);padding:0;\">\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 16px 12px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#cf4436;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">牛逼</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">马耳他政府刚刚消息：向全体国民提供免费的 AI 课程，以及免费的 ChatGPT Plus 会员。<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">马耳他成为首个</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">把 AI 作为全民基础服务来发放的国家</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:14px 0 8px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5592592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdh8o6ibAhHDm0cAXrsJN5ntibq9o9X5FOicrVRs8richKwWAMFpJuyrvgu0QiaaVYOkAs36tJQPia7hR4Gbh5x9gy0s3AONhhztviaRrM/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"215\" data-imgfileid=\"100033412\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7178a874&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdh8o6ibAhHDm0cAXrsJN5ntibq9o9X5FOicrVRs8richKwWAMFpJuyrvgu0QiaaVYOkAs36tJQPia7hR4Gbh5x9gy0s3AONhhztviaRrM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://mdia.gov.mt/services/ai-for-all-ai-ghal-kulhadd/\" target=\"_blank\">https://mdia.gov.mt/services/ai-for-all-ai-ghal-kulhadd/</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">项目名叫&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);\">AI for All</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（马耳他语 AI għal Kulħadd），意思是“全民 AI”。第一阶段五月启动，由马耳他数字创新管理局负责分发</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">马耳他的国民可以登录政府平台&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ai4all.gov.mt</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，先上完马耳他大学设计的 AI 素养课，三个核心模块通过之后，免费拿一年 ChatGPT Plus 订阅。课程和订阅都由政府出钱，参加者自己一分钱不花</span></p>\n    <div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);border-left:3px solid #cf4436;padding:8px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.8;margin: 0px 0px 8px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(207, 68, 54);font-weight: bold;\">有关马耳他</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.8;margin: 0px 0px 8px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">马耳他在地中海中部，意大利西西里岛以南，是英联邦、欧盟成员国、申根区国家</span><span leaf=\"\">，常住人口约 53 万</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8416666666666667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 0px auto;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdjEwqcTgbGiaaqoiafvfdibZFWZEZibusbcMBp5ibMb9Cyziaegl4xniaGWEmXiccpSbiaffu1d5wIpeySGWiaCSicv05pW3UURaXl0y2cGpk/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"503\" data-cropsely2=\"281\" data-backw=\"503\" data-backh=\"423\" data-imgfileid=\"100033413\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b9bc2615&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjEwqcTgbGiaaqoiafvfdibZFWZEZibusbcMBp5ibMb9Cyziaegl4xniaGWEmXiccpSbiaffu1d5wIpeySGWiaCSicv05pW3UURaXl0y2cGpk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.4;color:#cf4436;margin:18px 0 16px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么参加</span></h2>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;color:#1a1a18;margin:28px 0 6px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">资格</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.9;margin: 16px 0px 14px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">马耳他公民和居民，有可用的 eID 账户即可。无 AI 基础也能参加</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方页面点名欢迎的人群包括：在校学生、家长、教师、求职者、转行者、创作者、创业者、专业人士、商界领袖、还有想在网上更有信心的老人...换句话说，欢迎全民参与</span></p>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;color:#1a1a18;margin:28px 0 6px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">课程</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.9;margin: 16px 0px 4px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">由马耳他大学设计，全程在线，全程免费。三个核心模块必修：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"padding:0 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 基础</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">与批判性使用</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">日常生活</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">中的 AI</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">学习</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">中的 AI</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.9;margin: 16px 0px 4px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">之后可继续选修其他模块，每完成一个再拿一张证书。可选的有：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"padding:0 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 与职业</span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 与求职</span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 与创业</span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 与无障碍</span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;margin-right:10px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 与正式教育</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">面向教师、家长、学校</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;color:#1a1a18;margin:28px 0 6px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">学完能干什么</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.9;margin: 16px 0px 4px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方明确列了四条：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"padding:0 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;识别不可靠或误导性的 AI 输出</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;保护个人隐私和数据</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 10px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(120,120,112,0.18);\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;用 AI 更高效地学习和创作</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:10px 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;margin:0;line-height:1.8;word-break:break-all;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#cf4436;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;判断什么时候该用 AI、什么时候不该用</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;color:#1a1a18;margin:28px 0 6px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">证书和订阅</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.9;margin: 16px 0px 14px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过三个核心模块拿到第一张证书，同时获得&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 24);font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT Plus 一年免费订阅</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。每完成一个额外模块再拿一张证书</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">订阅由项目指定平台提供，目前公布的是 ChatGPT Plus。一年免费期之后，官方没说续费安排</span></p>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;color:#1a1a18;margin:28px 0 6px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">注册</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.9;margin: 16px 0px 14px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">平台用 eID 单点登录，入口是&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family: &quot;JetBrains Mono&quot;, &quot;SF Mono&quot;, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;font-size: 13.5px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);background: rgba(26, 26, 24, 0.06);padding: 1px 5px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ai4all.gov.mt</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。课程和订阅都还在开发中，官方说“未来几个月内上线”</span></p>\n    <h3 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.4;color:#1a1a18;margin:28px 0 6px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">合作伙伴</span></h3>\n    <p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(74, 74, 69);line-height: 1.9;margin: 16px 0px 14px;word-break: break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">这件事是和 OpenAI 的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 24);font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI for Countries</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;业务线对接做的，负责人是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(26, 26, 24);font-weight: 600;\"><span leaf=\"\">George Osborne</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（前英国财政大臣）。该业务线已经在和爱沙尼亚、希腊合作国家级教育系统</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.9;margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">马耳他这边签约的是经济、企业与战略项目部部长&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color:#1a1a18;font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Silvio Schembri</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.4;color:#cf4436;margin:18px 0 16px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">常见问题</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：现在能注册了吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：还没，平台和课程在开发中，官方说未来几个月内上线</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：我不是马耳他人能领吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：不能，仅限马耳他公民和居民</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：需要 AI 基础吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：不需要，课程从零起步</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：课程要钱吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：不要</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：怎么访问课程？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：登录在线平台&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13.5px;color:#007aaa;background:rgba(26,26,24,0.06);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ai4all.gov.mt</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，用 eID 单点登录</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：课程有时间安排吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：没有，全程在线，自己安排进度</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：不上课直接领订阅可以吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：不行，必须先完成三个核心模块</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：可以选别的 AI 平台吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：不行，订阅由项目指定平台提供</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：以前上过的 AI 课能退款吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：不能，本项目只涵盖新开发的课程</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：已有 ChatGPT 订阅可以退款或抵扣吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：不行</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：可以多选几个选修模块吗？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：可以，每完成一个发一张证书</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#1a1a18;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 2px;font-weight:600;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Q：证书有什么用？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#4a4a45;line-height:1.8;margin:0 0 20px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">A：证明完成了课程，三个核心模块发一张，每选修一个再发一张</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=29aa12a9&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzkzNDQxOTU2MQ%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247517066%26idx%3D1%26sn%3D0b407e1797ba301455ccb1ff42e8eb04\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "马耳他政府推出「全民 AI」计划，向全体公民和居民免费提供 AI 素养课程和一年 ChatGPT Plus 订阅，成为首个将 AI 作为全民基础服务发放的国家。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "马耳他政府推出「全民 AI」计划，向全体公民和居民免费提供 AI 素养课程和一年 ChatGPT Plus 订阅，成为首个将 AI 作为全民基础服务发放的国家。",
  "summary": "马耳他政府宣布启动「AI for All」项目，向全体公民和居民免费提供由马耳他大学设计的 AI 素养课程，完成三个核心模块后即可获得一年免费 ChatGPT Plus 订阅。课程涵盖 AI 基础、日常生活与学习场景的应用，以及职业发展、创业等选修模块。该项目与 OpenAI 的「OpenAI for Countries」业务线合作，由马耳他数字创新管理局负责分发。文章详细介绍了参与资格、课程内容、证书获取方式及常见问题，强调该项目从零起步、全程在线、完全免费，旨在提升全民 AI 素养和批判性使用能力。",
